      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hafs Bin Bakhtary, and someone else, ",
          "from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘It is disliked for the man that he should descend into the grave of his son’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "2. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Um ay r from Hafs ibn al-Bakhtariy and others who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said that it is undesirable for a man to enter the grave of his sons.” "
        ]
      }
